      "document_id": "doc_m1002_case_a",
      "unit_type": "paragraph",
      "sequence_no": 1,
      "text": "中芯国际发布2025年年度报告：销售收入约578.3亿元，净利润约86.5亿元，晶圆出货量882万片，毛利率24.5%。",
      "locator": {
        "paragraph_no": 1
      },
      "speaker": "中芯国际"
    },
    {
      "id": "cu_m1002_a_p2",
      "object_type": "content_unit",
      "schema_version": "1.0",
      "created_by": "manual_fixture",
      "workspace_id": "m1_002",
      "language": "zh-CN",
      "privacy_level": "public",
      "tags": [
        "M1-002",
        "中芯国际"
      ],
      "provenance": {
        "origin_type": "derived",
        "origin_object_ids": [
          "cu_m1002_c_p15",
          "cu_m1002_c_p16"
        ],
        "derivation_note": "PR段落由年报内容摘要而来",
        "source_locator_required": true,
        "processing_run_id": "run_m1002_manual_mapping"
      },
      "document_id": "doc_m1002_case_a",
      "unit_type": "paragraph",
      "sequence_no": 2,
      "text": "28nm及以上成熟制程收入占比76%，14nm/12nm FinFET占比18%；资本开支75.6亿美元。",
      "locator": {
        "paragraph_no": 2
      },
      "speaker": "中芯国际"
    },
    {
      "id": "cu_m1002_a_p3",
